channel.title: Advertise To My Audience! - 2,225+ YouTube Subscribers, 1 MILLION views!
channel.description:
Hey everyone! I have 2,222+ subscribers on YouTube. Over the last 6 years, I have gained a lot of views... almost 1 million. I want to try helping people out, by helping myself out at the same time. If you have a video advertisement of your RSPS, and want it advertised on my YouTube channel, I will gladly talk to you about it. Please contact me on Skype, or reply with your Skype username.
Skype: rambobarnes
YouTube link: [url=http://www.youtube.com/CodyChrisProductions]www.youtube.com/CodyChrisProductions[/url]
SIDE NOTE: Just because I have over 2,200 subscribers, that DOES NOT mean that you will get 2,200 players, or even 2,200+ views on the video. It just means that the video will automatically be sent to 2,200+ people. Yes, most of my subscribers play RSPS/OSRS/New RS, but some of them do not even play RS.
